<div class="com-share" data-id="2043" data-title="《出版社谈了好几年电子书，但离未来还是很远》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/2043/medium/2043.jpg?1436647555" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/2043.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
